OOC: Okay guys, I am not quite sure where Megs was at, so here is what I
remember, if I missed something, tell me. Also

1. Luker, are the pods still out there?

2. I know Yan isnt here right now, but if you read this later, Stratus
was ordered to go with Astrotrain, he should know where to go.

3. rAuq, get off your ass and post.

4. I already told Perceptor to go with Triggerhappy and Skullgrin.

BIC:

Megatron turned to Blindchaos and Dominjoe. "The tour will have to wait,
I have urgent things to attend to." he told them, then headed towards
the elevator. "I can however use your help." he told them.
